Integration runtime: is the compute infrastructure. An integration runtime provides the bridge between activities and linked services. 
Three types:
Azure integration runtime
Self-hosted integration runtime
Azure-SQL Server Integration Services (SSIS) integration runtime


Validation Activity:
--------------------
Is used to ensure the pipeline only continue execution once it has validated.Timeout->Waiting for file at this time duration if file not recevide then validation activity will timeout.
Sleep->if you put 10 then it will check every 10 seconds for the file.
